dcterms:description: A dataset of Max-Cut instances used to demonstrate the presence of strict complementarity in real-world instances and to evaluate the performance of the proposed optimization methods.
dcterms:title: Max-Cut instances

dcterms:description: The Gset dataset is a collection of sparse matrices from the University of Florida Sparse Matrix Collection, used in various numerical experiments.
dcterms:title: Gset dataset

dcterms:description: Graphs G1 to G20 are specific instances from the Gset dataset, utilized in the context of Max-Cut problems to evaluate the proposed optimization methods.
dcterms:title: Graphs G1 to G20
